data.rationale:
I was originally going to put it in Games::Pathfinding but thought
    it could possibly be more generally useful so moved it to AI. I
    couldn't find a similar module anywhere else in CPAN so I decided to
    upload what I came up with. This is my very first attempt at a CPAN
    contribution so any feedback is appreciated. Thank you for your
    time.
